check_mk Multiside extension to manage the user visibility.

This extension is a mutiside snapin, which is installable via 'add snapin to the sidebar' button.

The snapin manage the visibility of Hosts/Services that you see only host and services that the user is a contact for yes/no.

Any feedback welcome, PM to karsten.schoeke[at]geobasis-bb[dot]de. 
I'm also reading the german check_mk ML: checkmk-de@lists.mathias-kettner.de

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

Install the lgb_visibility_control-x.x.mkp package on multiside server.
